---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Performance Programming - Kalthoff Performance">
  <section class="min-h-screen bg-black text-white py-20">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-4xl">
      <h1 class="text-6xl font-black mb-8 tracking-tight">Performance Programming</h1>
      
      <div class="relative w-full h-[400px] mb-12 rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
        <img 
          src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1534438327276-14e5300c3a48?q=80&w=2070&auto=format&fit=crop" 
          alt="Athlete performing strength training" 
          class="w-full h-full object-cover"
          loading="lazy"
          decoding="async"
          width="2070"
          height="1380"
        />
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/60 to-transparent"></div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="prose prose-lg prose-invert max-w-none">
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 mb-8">
          My approach to performance training is built on the principles of strength, speed, power, and endurance, tailored to the specific demands of each sport and individual. With extensive experience across multiple sports, I integrate cutting-edge strength and conditioning techniques to help athletes and active individuals reach their peak potential. Using TeamBuildr—an advanced online programming platform—I design customized training programs that optimize performance, whether for competitive sports, personal fitness goals, or overall well-being. My focus is on creating structured, data-driven programs that ensure measurable progress and long-term success.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mt-12 mb-6">What's Included</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-4 text-gray-300">
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white mt-1 mr-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
            </svg>
            <span>Customized training programs based on your specific sport and position</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white mt-1 mr-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
            </svg>
            <span>Periodization planning to peak for important competitions</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white mt-1 mr-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
            </svg>
            <span>Performance testing and monitoring protocols</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white mt-1 mr-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
            </svg>
            <span>Regular program adjustments based on progress and feedback</span>
          </li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mt-12 mb-6">Program Delivery</h2>
        <div class="bg-white/5 rounded-lg p-6 mb-12">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Powered by TeamBuildr</h3>
          <img src="/images/full-logo-white-orange.png" alt="TeamBuildr Logo" class="h-12 mb-6" />
          <p class="text-gray-300">
            All programming is delivered through TeamBuildr, a professional training app that provides:
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-4 text-gray-300 mt-4">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white mt-1 mr-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
              </svg>
              <span>Easy-to-follow workout instructions with video demonstrations</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white mt-1 mr-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
              </svg>
              <span>Progress tracking and performance metrics</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white mt-1 mr-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
              </svg>
              <span>Direct communication with your coach</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mt-12 mb-6">Who Is This For?</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-4 text-gray-300">
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white mt-1 mr-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
            </svg>
            <span>Elite and professional athletes</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white mt-1 mr-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
            </svg>
            <span>Competitive amateur athletes</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white mt-1 mr-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
            </svg>
            <span>Athletes looking to reach the next level in their sport</span>
          </li>
        </ul>

        <div class="mt-12 bg-white/5 rounded-lg p-8 border border-white/10">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Ready to Elevate Your Performance?</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-300 mb-8">
            Take the first step towards achieving your peak performance potential with our expert programming.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
            <a href="/pricing" class="inline-block bg-white text-black px-8 py-3 rounded-full text-lg font-bold tracking-wide hover:bg-gray-200 transition duration-300">
              View Pricing
            </a>
            <a href="/contact" class="inline-block bg-white/10 text-white px-8 py-3 rounded-full text-lg font-bold tracking-wide hover:bg-white/20 transition duration-300">
              Contact Us
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout> 